'58','','1','Matt','70.89.197.145','matt@attackvector.org','http://www.attackvector.org','@bukmacher:  We would have to discuss what it is that you\'d want to submit, your technical background, and stuff like that.  I wouldn\'t let someone whom I didn\'t know post articles without me first grilling them to see if they know what they\'re talking about.  ;-)\n\nAlso, do you have access to the configuration file of the Squid proxy that you\'re using?  If so, you may want to make some changes because there are some seriously major flaws in the configuration that you\'re using.','2010-06-09 08:46:06','2010-06-09 13:46:06','0','57','110','','2'),(
