'195','','1','Erik','153.9.5.205','hortonew@gmail.com','http://n/a','Hey Matt,\n\nthis time i provided my real email, haha.\n\nI actually went for my bachelors in network administration, got 2 minors in web development, and info sec.  I suck at design - more of the programming, development type.  So my education is in the network side of things, but my experience and jobs have always been in web development.\n\nMy school didn\'t have a full blown security program otherwise I would have taken it, but I did get the most out of a few computer forensics, and host &amp; network security classes.\n\nI like the web attacks idea.  I have done a legitimate pentest on my old jobs website for SQL injection - not a full test but a test nonetheless.  It would be cool to see what you have to say on the subject.\n\nTake it easy and feel free to send an email my way for further discussions.\n-Erik','2010-05-27 08:07:30','2010-05-27 13:07:30','0','0','267','','0'),(
