'233','','1','Sie','20.138.1.245','vickers.j.simon@sky.com','','Hi Matt, thanks for the post, it cleared up a few questions I had! Got me wondering if mobile phone companies use static or dynamic ip\'s, and what resulting headers would be from them. Right im off to go email myself!!','2010-06-10 06:17:45','2010-06-10 11:17:45','0','0','299','','0'),(
