'263','','1','Erik','153.9.5.205','hortonew@gmail.com','http://n/a','and I was just thinking about asking you to discuss the use of proxies, haha. great stuff as usual, and lol\'d at work reading your windows comments. I do have suggestions for other posts if you\'d like to consider.  I was wondering if you could discuss the usages of  proxies through penetration testing, any benefits to IDS evasion, or will they most likely be on a block list, etc. Particularly have you used one with nmap before with the -g switch for which port you\'re sending it through?  take care.','2010-06-16 10:55:39','2010-06-16 15:55:39','0','0','329','','0'),(
