'275','','1','bwana','71.184.212.238','topjetboy@gmail.com','','thanks for writing this up. if i put myself in manning\'s shoes, why wouldn\'t denial work? After all, it\'s llamo\'s word against his, and llamo has been in the slammer. Unless wikileaks corroborated the evidence?\n\nI mean, couldn\'t llamo have gotten more press by naming, say, mitnick? or perhaps Obama\'s daughter?\n\nWhy wouldn\'t the authorities say that llamo\'s intimate knowledge of the event pointed the finger back to himself?\n\nI am not trying to be ridonculous, just want to know.','2010-06-19 15:37:08','2010-06-19 20:37:08','0','0','355','','0'),(
