'296','','1','Matt','70.89.197.145','matt@attackvector.org','http://www.attackvector.org','@nick:  It looks like when I pasted the code, my theme removed the \"STDIN\" in between the brackets in the while statement.  So, it should look like this:\n\n\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\n\nnmap --script=smb-enum-users 192.168.0.3 -p 445|perl -le \'while(<STDIN>){if(/^.*?\\(w+)s+.*/) { print \"$1\"; }}\' >> userlist\n\n\n</pre>','2010-09-22 07:39:17','2010-09-22 12:39:17','0','295','359','','2'),(
