'577','','1','Matt','70.89.197.145','matt@attackvector.org','http://www.attackvector.org','@Joe:  I just copied &amp; pasted the script from the blog to a file and ran it and didn\'t get any errors.  Not sure what would be causing that error.  Are you sure it copy &amp; pasted correctly? (ie - no word wrapping/etc?)\n\nAnd, the url (api.skyhook...) is still valid.. the connect error is probably related to the parser error.\n\nCan you paste the entire output of the command?','2010-09-24 11:43:12','2010-09-24 16:43:12','0','575','613','','2'),(
