oved over all of the site content I could. I dont think the user accounts moved over properly so users may have to register again. If you have any issues, shoot me a message to <a href=\"mailto:bobby@attackvector.org\">bobby@attackvector.org</a>.\n\nIm going to keep the website looking the sameminus the advertisements. Im not a big fan of the Google Ads, Ill keep one small banner up for my site TunnelGuard and thats about it.\n\nIll try to post regularly and share my thoughts and ideas with the info security world. I have some friends with similar mindsets as well so Ill see if any of them would be interested in blogging as well.\n\nIf there are security minded people following this blog who would be interested in blogging periodically, send me an email!\n\nBobby','','2012-05-07 15:18:00','2012-05-07 15:18:00','','','2012-05-07 15:18:00','2012-05-07 15:18:00','658-revision','658','','inherit','AttackVector.org - Under New Management _','revision',''),(
